These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-1::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: coffee, cola, iced-tea, lemonade, milk, soy-milk
The people have 6 different jobs:  teacher, engineer, doctor, designer, dancer, dressmaker
1. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the dancer##1
2. the designer is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
3. the engineer is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
4. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
5. the engineer is on the left of the dressmaker##1
6. the designer is on the left of the doctor##1
7. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
8. the dancer is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2    |      3      |     4     |     5     |    6    |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | coffee  | iced-tea    | lemonade  | cola      | milk    |
| Job      | engineer  | dressmaker | dancer | teacher | designer | doctor |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-2::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: action, disaster, drama, family, romance, sports
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, chaman, swisher, siglo, fonseca, bluemaster
1. the siglo-smoker is on the left of the fonseca-smoker##1
2. the bluemaster-smoker is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
3. the vegafina-smoker is on the left of the bluemaster-smoker##1
4. the swisher-smoker is on the far left##1
5. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the siglo-smoker##1
6. the chaman-smoker is on the right of the swisher-smoker##1
7. the person watching sports movies is the bluemaster-smoker##1
8. the bluemaster-smoker is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
9. the person watching action movies is the swisher-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3     |   4    |     5      |   6    |
| Movie-Genre   | action   | romance | disaster | sports | family     | drama  |
| Cigar           | swisher | chaman    | vegafina      | bluemaster  | siglo | fonseca |

