.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-4::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: epic, crime, horror, fantasy, mystery, action
The people use 6 different means of transport: airplane, bike, helicopter, ship, snowmobile, taxi
1. the person driving the airplane is on the far left##1
2. the person watching horror movies is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
4. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
5. the person driving the taxi is the person watching fantasy movies##1
6. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
7. the person watching mystery movies is on the far right##1
8. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2   |     3      |     4      |   5   |    6    |
| Movie-Genre   | horror  | fantasy | epic      | crime  | action | mystery |
| Transport     | airplane | taxi  | snowmobile | helicopter | ship  | bike    |

