.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-5::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: baking, filmmaking, hiking, singing, traveling, woodworking
The people use 6 different means of transport: taxi, roller, ship, subway, bike, snowmobile
 1. the person driving the ship is the person who's hobby is baking##1
 2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
 3. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 4. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
 5. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 6. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
 7. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
 8. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
 9. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
10. the person who's hobby is singing is the person driving the snowmobile##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4     |     5      |    6    |
| Hobby         | singing | woodworking | baking | traveling | filmmaking | hiking  |
| Transport   | snowmobile  | subway  | ship  | taxi | bike      | roller |

