.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-7::.
6 different pets are kept: chinchilla, dog, guinea-pig, horse, snake, turtle
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: skateboarding, golf, cricket, climbing, weightlifting, tennis
1. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
4. the owner of the horse is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
5. the owner of the horse is the person who's sport is tennis##1
6. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person who's sport is cricket##1
7. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
8. the owner of the dog is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2      |   3   |     4      |   5   |     6      |
| Pet         | dog       | turtle     | horse | guinea-pig | snake | chinchilla |
| Sport   | golf | weightlifting | tennis | cricket     | skateboarding  | climbing       |

