.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-8::.
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: ambient, funk, hip-hop, punk, reggae, salsa
There are 6 different favourite beverages: tea, water, 7up, milk, almond-milk, iced-tea
1. the fan of hip-hop is the person drinking almond-milk##1
2. the person drinking iced-tea is the fan of punk##1
3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the fan of funk##1
4. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
5. the person drinking water is the fan of salsa##1
6. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
7. the fan of ambient is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
8. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2     |     3      |     4      |   5   |       6       |
| Music-Genre   | salsa | ambient  | reggae     | hip-hop    | funk  | punk          |
| Beverage         | water  | tea | 7up | almond-milk | milk | iced-tea |

