6. the fisherman is on the far right##1
7. the indonesian is the manager##1
8. the indian is on the right of the japanese##1
9. the pilot is on the left of the librarian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |   3   |      4      |    5     |     6     |
| Nationality   | spanish    | indonesian     | brazilian | japanese | indian | italian   |
| Job        | writer | manager | pilot | librarian   | coach    | fisherman |

