3. the person driving the roller is on the left of the old-henry-smoker##1
4. the old-henry-smoker is the person driving the motorbike##1
5. the prince-smoker is on the right of the person driving the car##1
6. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the prince-smoker##1
7. the baccarat-smoker is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
8. the person driving the car is on the far left##1
9. the blend-smoker is the person driving the trike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |     2     |       3        |     4     |     5     |   6    |
| Cigar         | baccarat | prince | siglo | oliveros | old-henry    | blend |
| Transport   | car   | tram      | scooter        | roller    | motorbike | trike  |

