1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is the person who's birthday is in october##1
2. the person who's birthday is in december is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
3. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
4. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
5. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
6. the person who's hobby is reading is on the far left##1
7. the person who's hobby is video-games is the person who's birthday is in may##1
8. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
9. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1        |        2        |   3    |     4      |      5       |    6    |
| Hobby   | reading        | video-games     | chess  | filmmaking | magic-tricks | dancing |
| Birthday     | july | may | january | december  | october      | november    |

