.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-20::.
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: country, funk, house, metal, rock, salsa
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: badminton, skiing, cricket, skateboarding, snowboarding, swimming
1. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
2. the fan of salsa is on the right of the fan of funk##1
3. the fan of rock is on the left of the fan of house##1
4. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the fan of metal##1
5. the fan of rock is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
6. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
7. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
8. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
9. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |     2     |     3      |   4    |   5   |     6      |
| Music-Genre   | funk | salsa     | rock       | house  | metal | country    |
| Sport     | swimming  | badminton | skiing | skateboarding | snowboarding  | cricket |

 